<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>White marble fragment  of a <rs type="objectType" cert="low">sarcophagus</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.15</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.35</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.45</measure>) with a <rs type="decoration">bust</rs> in relief.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> to the right of the bust.</p>
</div>
